---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="See The System | Badmouth Digital" description="Every lead follows a path. Nothing depends on you remembering to do it." currentPage="see-the-system">

    <!-- SECTION 1 — HERO -->
    <section class="section section--hero surface-base noise-bg has-scanlines" style="position: relative; min-height: auto; padding-top: var(--space-24); padding-bottom: var(--space-16);">
        <div class="grid-page grid-align-center">

            <!-- Left Column: Copy -->
            <div class="col-half-left stack-4" style="position: relative; z-index: 5; padding-right: var(--space-4);">
                <p class="t-eyebrow" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                    <span class="status-dot status-dot--live"></span>
                    <span class="sys-path">> /sys/pipeline/overview</span>
                </p>
                <h1 class="t-display t-display--hero">
                    EVERY LEAD<br />
                    <span class="t-crt-shake" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">FOLLOWS</span><br />
                    <span class="t-flicker" style="color: var(--color-brand);">A PATH.</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="t-body t-body--lg" style="max-width: 52ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    Nothing depends on you remembering to do it.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 52ch;">
                    Most contractors have a pile of disconnected tools. Website that doesn't track anything. CRM they signed up for and never opened. Call tracking from two vendors ago. None of it talks to each other.
                </p>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="max-width: 52ch; color: var(--color-text-primary); font-weight: 600;">
                    We wire it all into one system. Here's what each piece does and how it connects.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Column: System Pipeline Graphic -->
            <div class="col-half-right" style="perspective: 1200px; position: relative; z-index: 5; padding-left: var(--space-4);">
                <div class="browser-mockup" style="transform: rotateY(-5deg) rotateX(2deg); box-shadow: -20px 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.8), 0 0 40px rgba(79,209,197,0.12);">
                    <div class="browser-mockup__header">
                        <div class="browser-controls">
                            <span class="dot dot--red"></span>
                            <span class="dot dot--yellow"></span>
                            <span class="dot dot--green"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="browser-url">badmouth.digital/sys-pipeline</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="browser-mockup__body mech-flicker">
                        <div class="mech-ink-overlay"></div>

                        <div class="mech-container" style="padding: 14px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; min-height: 420px;">

                            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
                                <div>
                                    <span class="mech-label red-accent" style="display:block; margin-bottom:3px;">Pipeline Architecture</span>
                                    <div style="font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: 0.05em; color: #fff; line-height: 1;">LEAD_PATH<span class="red-accent"> V.09</span></div>
                                </div>
                                <div style="text-align:right; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px;">
                                    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1px;">
                                        <span class="mech-label" style="display:block;">Leads Processed</span>
                                        <div class="mech-value green-accent" id="sysLeadCounter" style="font-size: 0.85rem;">0</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-end; gap: 1px;">
                                        <span class="mech-label" style="display:block;">Uptime</span>
                                        <div class="mech-value" id="sysUptime" style="font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">00h 00m 00s</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; flex: 1;">

                                <div class="sys-pipe-node sys-pipe-node--entry" id="pipeNode1">
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-icon" style="color: var(--color-brand, #ff003c);">▶</div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-content">
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-label">LEAD ARRIVES</span>
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-tag red-accent">INBOUND</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-status red-accent">LIVE</div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="sys-pipe-arrow"><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__line"></div><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__packet" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;"></div></div>

                                <div class="sys-pipe-node" id="pipeNode2">
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-icon" style="color: var(--color-brand, #ff003c);">◎</div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-content">
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-label">SERVICE PAGES</span>
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-tag" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">CONVERTS TRAFFIC</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-status green-accent">OK</div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="sys-pipe-arrow"><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__line"></div><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__packet" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;"></div></div>

                                <div class="sys-pipe-node" id="pipeNode3">
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-icon" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal, #4fd1c5);">◎</div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-content">
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-label">LEAD CAPTURE</span>
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-tag" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">EVERY CALL. EVERY FORM.</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-status green-accent">OK</div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="sys-pipe-arrow"><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__line"></div><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__packet" style="animation-delay: 1.4s;"></div></div>

                                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6px;">
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-node sys-pipe-node--sm" id="pipeNode4">
                                        <div class="sys-pipe-icon" style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow, #f6c90f); font-size: 0.65rem;">◎</div>
                                        <div class="sys-pipe-content">
                                            <span class="sys-pipe-label" style="font-size: 0.5rem;">AUTO FOLLOW-UP</span>
                                            <span class="sys-pipe-tag" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); font-size: 0.42rem;">SMS + EMAIL</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="sys-pipe-status green-accent" style="font-size: 0.45rem;">RUN</div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-node sys-pipe-node--sm" id="pipeNode5">
                                        <div class="sys-pipe-icon" style="color: var(--color-brand, #ff003c); font-size: 0.65rem;">◎</div>
                                        <div class="sys-pipe-content">
                                            <span class="sys-pipe-label" style="font-size: 0.5rem;">REVIEW ENGINE</span>
                                            <span class="sys-pipe-tag" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); font-size: 0.42rem;">AUTO-REQUEST</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="sys-pipe-status green-accent" style="font-size: 0.45rem;">RUN</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="sys-pipe-arrow"><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__line"></div><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__packet" style="animation-delay: 2.0s;"></div></div>

                                <div class="sys-pipe-node" id="pipeNode6">
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-icon" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal, #4fd1c5);">◎</div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-content">
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-label">TRACKING + ATTRIBUTION</span>
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-tag" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">EVERY SOURCE LOGGED</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-status green-accent">OK</div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="sys-pipe-arrow"><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__line"></div><div class="sys-pipe-arrow__packet" style="animation-delay: 2.6s;"></div></div>

                                <div class="sys-pipe-node sys-pipe-node--terminal" id="pipeNode7">
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-icon" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal, #4fd1c5);">▣</div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-content">
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-label">DASHBOARD</span>
                                        <span class="sys-pipe-tag" style="color: rgba(79,209,197,0.7);">ONE SCREEN. ALL NUMBERS.</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="sys-pipe-status" style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal); font-weight:900;">LIVE</div>
                                </div>

                            </div>

                            <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding-top: 8px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
                                <span style="font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace); font-size: 0.45rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);">&gt; SYS_STATUS: ALL NODES ACTIVE</span>
                                <span class="mech-cursor"></span>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="scroll-indicator">
            <span class="scroll-indicator__label">Scroll</span>
            <span class="scroll-indicator__chevron"></span>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TICKER STRIP -->
    <div class="sys-ticker" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="sys-ticker__track">
            <span>LEAD CAPTURED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>INSTANT TEXT-BACK SENT</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>FOLLOW-UP QUEUED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>CRM UPDATED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>REVIEW REQUESTED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>SOURCE ATTRIBUTED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>DASHBOARD UPDATED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <!-- Duplicate for seamless loop -->
            <span>LEAD CAPTURED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>INSTANT TEXT-BACK SENT</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>FOLLOW-UP QUEUED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>CRM UPDATED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>REVIEW REQUESTED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>SOURCE ATTRIBUTED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
            <span>DASHBOARD UPDATED</span><span class="sys-ticker__sep">→</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        /* Terminal path eyebrow */
        .sys-path {
            font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            color: var(--theme-accent-teal);
            opacity: 0.8;
        }




        /* Scrolling ticker strip */
        .sys-ticker {
            overflow: hidden;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.15);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(79, 209, 197, 0.15);
            padding: 11px 0;
        }
        .sys-ticker__track {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            white-space: nowrap;
            animation: tickerScroll 28s linear infinite;
            font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace);
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.15em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
        }
        .sys-ticker__sep {
            color: var(--theme-accent-teal);
            opacity: 0.6;
        }
        @keyframes tickerScroll {
            0%   { transform: translateX(0); }
            100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
        }

        /* Pipeline node styles */
        .sys-pipe-node {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
            border-radius: 3px; padding: 8px 10px;
            opacity: 0; animation: nodeFadeIn 0.4s ease forwards;
        }
        .sys-pipe-node--entry { border-color: rgba(255,0,60,0.35); background: rgba(255,0,60,0.06); }
        .sys-pipe-node--terminal { border-color: rgba(79,209,197,0.35); background: rgba(79,209,197,0.06); }
        .sys-pipe-node--sm { padding: 6px 8px; }
        .sys-pipe-icon { font-size: 0.8rem; flex-shrink: 0; line-height: 1; }
        .sys-pipe-content { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; min-width: 0; }
        .sys-pipe-label { font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace); font-size: 0.55rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #fff; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
        .sys-pipe-tag { font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace); font-size: 0.44rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; white-space: nowrap; }
        .sys-pipe-status { font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace); font-size: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .sys-pipe-arrow { position: relative; height: 10px; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 12px; }
        .sys-pipe-arrow__line { position: absolute; left: 12px; right: 12px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(79,209,197,0.15) 0%, rgba(79,209,197,0.4) 50%, rgba(79,209,197,0.15) 100%); }
        .sys-pipe-arrow__line::after { content: '▶'; position: absolute; right: -6px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); font-size: 0.5rem; color: rgba(79,209,197,0.5); line-height: 1; }
        .sys-pipe-arrow__packet { position: absolute; left: 12px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 6px; height: 3px; background: var(--theme-accent-teal, #4fd1c5); border-radius: 1px; box-shadow: 0 0 6px var(--theme-accent-teal, #4fd1c5); animation: packetFlow 2.5s linear infinite; }
        @keyframes packetFlow { 0% { left: 12px; opacity: 0; } 10% { opacity: 1; } 90% { opacity: 1; } 100% { left: calc(100% - 18px); opacity: 0; } }
        @keyframes nodeFadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-6px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); } }
        #pipeNode1 { animation-delay: 0.1s; } #pipeNode2 { animation-delay: 0.4s; } #pipeNode3 { animation-delay: 0.8s; }
        #pipeNode4 { animation-delay: 1.2s; } #pipeNode5 { animation-delay: 1.4s; } #pipeNode6 { animation-delay: 1.6s; } #pipeNode7 { animation-delay: 2.0s; }

        /* ── Blinking block cursor ── */
        .sys-block-cursor {
            display: inline-block;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            animation: cursorBlink 1.1s step-end infinite;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-size: 0.3em;
            margin-left: 2px;
            vertical-align: sub;
        }
        @keyframes cursorBlink {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0; }
        }

        /* ── Module Card Enhancements ── */
        .sys-mod-card {
            position: relative;
            transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }
        .sys-mod-card:hover {
            border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--mod-color, var(--theme-accent-teal)) 50%, transparent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 18px color-mix(in srgb, var(--mod-color, var(--theme-accent-teal)) 15%, transparent),
                        inset 0 0 12px color-mix(in srgb, var(--mod-color, var(--theme-accent-teal)) 6%, transparent);
        }
        .sys-mod-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: var(--space-2);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
        }
        .sys-mod-meta {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-end;
            gap: 3px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        .sys-mod-id {
            font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace);
            font-size: 0.48rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .sys-status-badge {
            font-family: var(--font-mono, monospace);
            font-size: 0.48rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #00e676;
            background: rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.25);
            border-radius: 2px;
            padding: 1px 5px;
        }
        .sys-mod-bar {
            height: 2px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border-radius: 1px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-top: auto;
        }
        .sys-mod-bar__fill {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 1px;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .sys-stat-card {
            transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }
        .sys-stat-card:hover {
            border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--stat-color, var(--theme-accent-teal)) 50%, transparent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px color-mix(in srgb, var(--stat-color, var(--theme-accent-teal)) 15%, transparent),
                        inset 0 0 14px color-mix(in srgb, var(--stat-color, var(--theme-accent-teal)) 6%, transparent);
        }
        .sys-stagger {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(16px);
            transition:
                opacity 0.5s ease calc(var(--stagger, 0) * 120ms),
                transform 0.5s ease calc(var(--stagger, 0) * 120ms);
        }
        .sys-stagger.is-visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
        .sys-scan-line {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -60%;
            width: 60%;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--scan-color, white), transparent);
            opacity: 0.45;
            animation: scanSlide 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes scanSlide {
            0%   { left: -60%; }
            100% { left: 140%; }
        }
        .sys-before-after-bar {
            display: flex;
            gap: 3px;
            margin: var(--space-2) 0;
            height: 4px;
        }
        .sys-ba-before {
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
            border-radius: 1px;
        }
        .sys-ba-after {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 1px;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }
    </style>

    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            // Lead counter
            const counter = document.getElementById('sysLeadCounter');
            if (counter) {
                let val = 0;
                const target = 14872;
                const step = () => {
                    val += Math.floor(Math.random() * 800 + 200);
                    if (val >= target) { val = target; counter.textContent = val.toLocaleString(); return; }
                    counter.textContent = val.toLocaleString();
                    requestAnimationFrame(step);
                };
                step();
            }

            // Uptime counter
            const uptimeEl = document.getElementById('sysUptime');
            if (uptimeEl) {
                const start = Date.now();
                setInterval(() => {
                    const s = Math.floor((Date.now() - start) / 1000);
                    const h = String(Math.floor(s / 3600)).padStart(2, '0');
                    const m = String(Math.floor((s % 3600) / 60)).padStart(2, '0');
                    const sec = String(s % 60).padStart(2, '0');
                    uptimeEl.textContent = `${h}h ${m}m ${sec}s`;
                }, 1000);
            }
        });

        // Stagger reveal + counter animations
        const staggerEls = document.querySelectorAll('.sys-stagger');
        const obs = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
            entries.forEach(entry => {
                if (!entry.isIntersecting) return;
                entry.target.classList.add('is-visible');
                obs.unobserve(entry.target);

                const pair = entry.target.querySelector('.sys-count-pair');
                if (pair) {
                    const before = +pair.dataset.before;
                    const after  = +pair.dataset.after;
                    const suffix = pair.dataset.suffix || '';
                    const bEl = pair.querySelector('.sys-count-before');
                    const aEl = pair.querySelector('.sys-count-after');
                    let t = 0; const dur = 900;
                    const tick = () => {
                        t = Math.min(t + 16, dur);
                        const p = t / dur;
                        bEl.textContent = Math.round(before + (before * 0.4) * (1 - p)) + suffix;
                        aEl.textContent = Math.round(after  + (after  * 0.6) * (1 - p)) + suffix;
                        if (t < dur) requestAnimationFrame(tick);
                        else { bEl.textContent = before + suffix; aEl.textContent = after + suffix; }
                    };
                    setTimeout(() => requestAnimationFrame(tick), 200);
                }
            });
        }, { threshold: 0.2 });
        staggerEls.forEach(el => obs.observe(el));
    </script>

    <!-- SECTION 2 — SYSTEM COMPONENTS -->
    <section class="section section--padded surface-sunken">
        <div class="grid-page grid-gap-lg">
            <div class="col-full text-center stack-4">
                <p class="t-eyebrow"><span class="sys-path">> /sys/components</span></p>
                <h2 class="t-display t-display--section" style="margin-inline: auto;">
                    WHAT EACH <span class="t-accent t-flicker">PIECE DOES.</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="t-body t-body--md" style="margin-inline: auto; max-width: 55ch;">
                    Every component has a specific job. Every job runs automatically.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-full">
                <div class="inner-grid-3">

                    <div class="card sys-mod-card stack-3" style="--mod-color: var(--color-brand);">
                        <div class="sys-mod-header">
                            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                                <span style="color: var(--color-brand); font-size: 1.2rem;">◉</span>
                                <h3 class="t-display t-display--card" style="margin: 0;">SERVICE PAGES</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sys-mod-meta">
                                <span class="sys-mod-id">[MOD_01]</span>
                                <span class="sys-status-badge">ACTIVE</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">Dedicated pages for each service, built around what people actually search. Every page has one job: turn the visitor into a lead.</p>
                        <div class="sys-mod-bar"><div class="sys-mod-bar__fill" style="width: 78%; background: var(--color-brand);"></div></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card sys-mod-card stack-3" style="--mod-color: var(--theme-accent-yellow);">
                        <div class="sys-mod-header">
                            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                                <span style="color: var(--theme-accent-yellow); font-size: 1.2rem;">◉</span>
                                <h3 class="t-display t-display--card" style="margin: 0;">LOCAL PAGES</h3>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sys-mod-meta">
                                <span class="sys-mod-id">[MOD_02]</span>
                                <span class="sys-status-badge">ACTIVE</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="t-body t-body--sm">City and town pages that rank your business in every market you serve — not just one. Built to show up when someone searches in a specific neighborhood or zip code.</p>
                        <div class="sys-mod-bar"><div class="sys-mod-bar__fill" style="width: 62%; background: var(--theme-accent-yellow);"></div></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card sys-mod-card stack-3" style="--mod-color: var(--theme-accent-teal);">
                        <div class="sys-mod-header">
                            <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                                <span style="color: var(--theme-accent-teal); font-size: 1.2rem;">◉</span>
